    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<pre><div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\"><pre><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">sdk</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">TabControl</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n            <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">i</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Interaction.Triggers</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n                <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">i</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">EventTrigger</span> <span style=\"color:red\">EventName</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">SelectionChanged</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n                    <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">i</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">InvokeCommandAction</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Command</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">{Binding InternalTabsSwitchedCommand}</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span>  <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n                <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">i</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">EventTrigger</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n            <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">i</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Interaction.Triggers</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></pre>\r\n<pre><span><br></span></pre>\r\n<pre><span><pre><div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\"><pre><span style=\"color:blue\">public</span> DelegateCommand&lt;<span style=\"color:blue\">object</span>&gt; InternalTabsSwitchedCommand { <span style=\"color:blue\">get</span>; <span style=\"color:blue\">private</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">set</span>; }\r\nInternalTabsSwitchedCommand = <span style=\"color:blue\">new</span> DelegateCommand&lt;<span style=\"color:blue\">object</span>&gt;(OnSwitchTab);\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">public</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">void</span> OnSwitchTab(<span style=\"color:blue\">object</span> args)\r\n\t    {\r\n\t        \r\n\t    }\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></pre>\r\n</span></pre>\r\n<pre>I was expecting the eventArgs of the SelectionChanged event to be passed into the command. But its always null.  Is this the expected behaviour? There must be a way though.</pre>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Many Thanks,</p>\r\n<p>Houman</p>\r\n",
